name: CryptoSerpent #024
description: Vincent Van Gaal is an innovative artist who weeks before the explosion was trying to get to know the limits of art, for this reason he created the “Galactic Night”, a virtual reality NFT in which he has been trapped. Once his planet was destroyed, the painting has been lost. The only way he has to get back to real life is for someone to repaint it in exactly the same way that he did.
